'''拿撒勒人會'''（{{lang-en|'''Church of the Nazarene'''}}），或稱'''宣聖會'''，是[[基督教|基督教]][[福音派|福音派]]下的一個[[基督教派系|派系]]，出現於北美19世紀的[[聖潔運動|聖潔運動]]中，其成員常被稱為'''拿撒勒派'''（Nazarenes，[[拿撒勒人|拿撒勒人]]）。它是世界上最大的[[循道宗|循道宗-聖潔教派]]。<ref>"Pentecostalism", in ''Encyclopedia of Religion and Society'', eds. William H. Swatos and Peter Kivisto (Rowman Altamira, 1998):358.</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.encyclopediaofarkansas.net/encyclopedia/entry-detail.aspx?entryID=4330 |title=''The Encyclopedia of Arkansas History and Culture: Church of the Nazarene'' |publisher=Encyclopediaofarkansas.net |date= |accessdate=2014-06-23 |archive-date=2018-09-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180916094903/http://www.encyclopediaofarkansas.net/encyclopedia/entry-detail.aspx?entryID=4330 |dead-url=no }}</ref> 2014年9月末，該會在世界各地記有2,295,106會眾、29,395座教堂。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ncnnews.com/nphweb/html/ncn/article.jsp?sid=10005006&id=10014168 |title="General secretary releases 2014 stats", ''NCN News'' (December 10, 2014)  |access-date=2015-03-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141216013538/http://www.ncnnews.com/nphweb/html/ncn/article.jsp?sid=10005006&id=10014168 |archive-date=2014-12-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>"The Church of the Nazarene uses "world area" to describe countries and areas that are a part of a country, but may be known by a different name. More than 20 of the denomination's 159 world areas fall into this category, such as Guam, a U.S. territory on the Asia-Pacific Region." See [http://www.ncnnews.com/nphweb/html/ncn/article.jsp?sid=10000012&id=10013302 Nazarene Research Services releases stats on 30-year world area growth] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncnnews.com/nphweb/html/ncn/article.jsp?sid=10000012&id=10013302 |date=20141216013341 }}, ''NCN News'' (January 10, 2014).</ref>

[[美國宗教|美國]]的拿撒勒人會信徒最多，計有631,454人，<ref>[http://nazarene.org/files/docs/StatisticsAnnual.pdf "Church of the Nazarene Growth, 2004-2014 Annual Statistics from the General Secretary's Reports" ] {{Wayback|url=http://nazarene.org/files/docs/StatisticsAnnual.pdf |date=20150919023155 }}</ref> 其次是[[莫桑比克宗教|莫桑比克]]（157,119）、[[巴西宗教|巴西]]（111,694）、[[印度宗教|印度]]（107,175）、[[孟加拉國宗教|孟加拉國]]（79,550）、<ref name="engagemagazine.com">Gina Grate Pottenger, [http://engagemagazine.com/Magazine-Content/Articles/April-2010/Bangladesh--It-started-with-a-letter.aspx "Bangladesh: It Started with a Letter"] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100921151437/http://engagemagazine.com/Magazine-Content/Articles/April-2010/Bangladesh--It-started-with-a-letter.aspx |date=2010-09-21 }}, ''Engage'' 12 (April 21, 2010)</ref> [[危地馬拉宗教|危地馬拉]]（78,212）<ref>[http://www.ncnnews.com/nphweb/html/ncn/article.jsp?sid=10005114&id=10012977 "GMC Flags of the Nations: Guatemala"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncnnews.com/nphweb/html/ncn/article.jsp?sid=10005114&id=10012977 |date=20141216013539 }}, ''NCN Global News Summary'' (September 17, 2013)</ref> 和[[海地宗教|海地]]（64,071）。而人均教徒數最多的國家是[[佛得角|佛得角]]。<ref name="Membership Stats">{{cite web |url=http://www.adherents.com/largecom/com_naz.html |title=Membership Stats |publisher=Adherents.com |date= |accessdate=2014-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150318064605/http://www.adherents.com/largecom/com_naz.html |archive-date=2015-03-18 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

該會的宗旨依[[大使命|大使命]]將基督教傳播到世界各地，<ref name="244823 Manual 2005-09">{{cite web|url=http://media.premierstudios.com/nazarene/docs/Manual2005_09.pdf |title=244823 Manual 2005-09 |format=PDF |date= |accessdate=2014-06-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130302214359/http://media.premierstudios.com/nazarene/docs/Manual2005_09.pdf |archivedate=2013-03-02 }}</ref><ref>[http://www.nazarene.org/ministries/administration/visitorcenter/about/display.aspx About the Church's Mission]  {{webarchive|url=https://www.webcitation.org/5mq4i9mC6?url=http://www.nazarene.org/ministries/administration/visitorcenter/about/display.aspx |date=2010-01-17 }}. After a unanimous decision of the Board of General Superintendents in December 2006 to express the Church's mission more concisely.</ref> 自2001開始將自己的核心價值定義為：「Christian」（我們是基督徒）、「Holiness」（聖潔）、「Missional」（使命）。<ref name=autogenerated7>{{cite web |url=http://www.nazarenepastor.org/clergyeducation/portals/0/Naz%20History%20Polity/NHPFacGu.pdf |title=Church of the Nazarene - Clergy Development |publisher=Nazarenepastor.org |date= |accessdate=2014-06-23 |archive-date=2008-04-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080411024354/http://www.nazarenepastor.org/clergyeducation/portals/0/Naz%20History%20Polity/NHPFacGu.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.ct.org.tw/1214410 |title=拿撒勒人會牧者靈修特會 |publisher=基督教論壇報 |date=2008-03-25 |accessdate=2015-03-23 |archive-date=2020-12-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201203191357/https://www.ct.org.tw/1214410 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

該教會在35個國家、6個大陸運營者53個本科及研究生教育機構，<ref name="ncnnews1">[http://www.ncnnews.com/nphweb/html/ncn/article.jsp?id=10013391 "International Board of Education releases global statistics"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncnnews.com/nphweb/html/ncn/article.jsp?id=10013391 |date=20140222162322 }}, ''NCN News'' (February 13, 2014).</ref><ref name="Holiness Today 2010">"Highlights of the 87th Session of the General Board", ''Holiness Today'' (May/June 2010):26.</ref><ref name="ncnnews2">Eugénio R. Duarte, [http://www.ncnnews.com/nphweb/html/ncn/article.jsp?id=10010038 "ANNUAL REPORT OF THE BOARD OF GENERAL SUPERINTENDENTS TO THE 88TH GENERAL BOARD CHURCH OF THE NAZARENE February 2011"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ncnnews.com/nphweb/html/ncn/article.jsp?id=10010038 |date=20110714161405 }}, ''NCN News'' (February 27, 2011)</ref> 2013年拿撒勒人會學院和大學入學人數達50,390人。<ref name="nazarene1">{{cite web|url=http://nazarene.org/education/iboe/statistics/display.html |title=2013 Enrollment Statistics |publisher=Nazarene.org |date= |accessdate=2014-06-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120104090225/http://nazarene.org/education/iboe/statistics/display.html |archivedate=2012-01-04 }}</ref> 該會的總部位於美國[[密蘇里州|密蘇里州]]的[[堪薩斯城_(密蘇里州)|堪薩斯城]]。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nazarene.org/ministries/administration/gmc/display.aspx |title=1 About the GMC |publisher=Nazarene.org |date= |accessdate=2014-06-23 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110929222837/http://www.nazarene.org/ministries/administration/gmc/display.aspx |archivedate=2011-09-29 }}</ref>

